---
title: Parmesan Pork Schnitzel & Creamy Lemon Herb Sauce with Spiced Wedges & Garden Salad
description: All the classic flavours in this German-inspired dish play off against each other in the most delightful way. The sweetness of the
apple with irresistible spiced wedges and crunchy Parmesan-coated pork is just lovely!
